# macOS
.DS_Store
._.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# sed leftovers (workspace couldn't delete these)
*.bak

# Per-user calibration data — should never be committed to a shared repo.
# Each user's calibration lives on their machine; only the README and _template.md
# are part of the plugin source.
**/calibration/[0-9]*.md
**/calibration/setup.md
**/calibration/profile.md

# Per-user references that get populated during first-run setup — these may
# contain personal voice samples, precedent docs, or tool config. Don't ship.
**/references/voice-guide.md
**/references/profile.md
**/references/template.md
**/references/examples/
**/references/sample-memos/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# Build artifacts
*.plugin
/tmp/

# Internal deployment notes — never commit
PUBLISHING.md
